title: From this day forth, we shall be known as...
body:
🌱

The Office of The SUSU has collected all the entries for our CarbonSwap Community naming contest. There were 142 members who submitted 325 names in total!  But due to of all the awesomeness, snapshot couldn't handle it, and the community help determine a shortlist. 

We wanted as many voices and ideas as possible, and we're amazed at the creativity you all showed. A sincere thank you to each and every one of you.

Please read through this incredibly clever list and as a community, let's decide what we should call ourselves.
--------
____
PRIZES:

🥇 1st Place: 1000 SUSU
🥈 2nd Place: 750 SUSU
🥉 3rd Place: 500 SUSU

REMINDER:  Each vote will count as a single vote. All votes will be tallied up at the end of the voting period to determine the winners.

~ Stay tuned and happy voting! ~
